{"word":"βραδύνω","slug":"βραδύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>βραδύνω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βραδύς\">βραδύς</a></el>] <b><i>be slow</i> <a href='B:610 3:15'>1 Ti 3:15</a></b> here = <i>be delayed<b>.</b> </i>In<b> <a href='B:680 3:9'>2 Pt 3:9</a></b> the point is that God is not, as alleged, hesitant in fulfilling a promise. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:βραβεύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:βραδυπλοέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}